<% content_for :body do %>
Organise a time to deliver asbestos to La Collette by filling in a booking form at least seven working days before the delivery date.
Before delivering any commercial loads of asbestos you must notify the Waste Regulator.
Wrap and / or double bag the asbestos according to legal guidelines before you arrive at the reception in La Collette.
Delivery drivers must wear PPE when either tipping and / or off-loading. All loads will be tipped and / or off-loaded by the driver.
Read more about asbestos disposal, find out how much it costs to dispose of it and download a booking form on Gov.je
